sentences: Victor Grimmy Owusu (born July 20, 1987), better known by his stage name V.I.C., is an retired American rapper.
His single, "Get Silly", reached #29 on the Billboard Hot 100 chart in 2008.
V.I.C. was born Victor Grimmy Owusu in 1987 in Corona, Queens to a mother from New York City and a father from Ghana.
Later that year he moved with his family to the Atlanta suburb of College Park, Georgia.
